title: Dawg For A Day - Championship Week Reviewed
description:
I'm gonna be straight with you: I (Ryan) am pretty sleepy this morning so I did not go through the podcast for timestamps of what we discussed. I do know that we hit every conference championship game in some form or another, and that we did not let Iowa State almost losing to Drake escape our watch, and that this episode is brought to you by our friends at LEGO.
But I still love you and want you to do great things and I will hopefully time stamp the next episode!
